you'll never get to punish.

566
20:48:54,060 --> 20:48:55,500
Now pick.

567
20:48:57,340 --> 20:48:58,710
No.

568
20:48:59,860 --> 20:49:01,037
Fine.

569
20:49:01,157 --> 20:49:01,957
Stop!

570
20:49:02,001 --> 20:49:05,142
Just stop pointing that
gun at her head. Stop.

571
20:49:05,340 --> 20:49:08,082
- Then choose.
- I can't choose one.

572
20:49:08,100 --> 20:49:08,915
Five.

573
20:49:09,221 --> 20:49:10,810
- Four.
- Please!

574
20:49:11,192 --> 20:49:12,499
Three.

575
20:49:13,060 --> 20:49:14,270
Two.

576
20:49:15,415 --> 20:49:17,259
- One!
- All right!

577
20:49:17,260 --> 20:49:18,820
All right!

578
20:49:23,220 --> 20:49:24,606
Have you chosen?

579
20:49:25,180 --> 20:49:26,108
Yes.

580
20:49:26,228 --> 20:49:27,341
Then say it.

581
20:49:28,586 --> 20:49:30,419
Say her name.

582
20:49:33,580 --> 20:49:35,500
Say it now!

583
20:49:42,460 --> 20:49:43,809
Alice.

584
20:49:46,237 --> 20:49:47,419
Say it again.

585
20:49:53,540 --> 20:49:55,885
- Shoot Alice.
- Say it again!

586
20:49:57,558 --> 20:49:58,784
Alice.

587
20:49:59,860 --> 20:50:00,379
No!

588
20:50:08,620 --> 20:50:09,563
Oops.

589
20:50:10,364 --> 20:50:11,778
Sorry,

590
20:50:12,179 --> 20:50:13,974
