591
20:50:15,300 --> 20:50:17,791
Run! Run. Run. Get out of here. Run! Go on.

592
20:50:21,180 --> 20:50:22,980
Go!

593
20:50:24,773 --> 20:50:27,339
Now, if I let this go,

594
20:50:28,071 --> 20:50:31,443
