what you want, isn't it?

595
20:50:31,487 --> 20:50:35,116
- Eh? But if I apply pressure just here...
- No.

596
20:50:35,500 --> 20:50:37,280
- There's a good chance you'll live.
- No!

597
20:50:37,487 --> 20:50:39,670
Please. Please. Don't. Please.

598
20:50:39,683 --> 20:50:41,679
- Please.
- Beg me.

599
20:50:42,098 --> 20:50:44,056
- Beg me!
- I'm begging you.

600
20:50:44,100 --> 20:50:47,099
Then where's Natalie? Where is she?

601
20:50:47,100 --> 20:50:49,659
- Please.
- Come on, Tom. Come on, Tom.

602
20:50:49,660 --> 20:50:50,551
The medics are coming,

603
20:50:50,563 --> 20:50:52,459
