- No. It's true. It's true.

606
20:51:01,186 --> 20:51:04,621
- How do I know? Is it true?
- Please. Just let go. Please.

607
20:51:06,340 --> 20:51:08,100
- You're ready to go?
- Yeah,

608
20:51:08,100 --> 20:51:10,470
I'm ready. I'm ready. I'm ready.

609
20:51:11,659 --> 20:51:13,449
Please...

610
20:51:14,287 --> 20:51:15,883
Not on your nelly.

611
20:51:16,380 --> 20:51:17,653
Medic!

612
20:51:18,122 --> 20:51:19,743
- No!
- Medic!

613
20:51:23,530 --> 20:51:26,427
I need him alive, put
pressure right here. Here!

614
20:51:39,180 --> 20:51:40,579
All right, upstairs.

615
20:51:40,580 --> 20:51:41,478
Sir.

616
20:51:58,580 --> 20:52:00,023
Natalie?

617
20:52:05,369 --> 20:52:07,300
We're the police.

618
20:52:12,500 --> 20:52:14,157
You're safe now.

619
20:52:31,180 --> 20:52:33,205
Hold on, hold on.

620
20:52:51,900 --> 20:52:53,120
Boss.

621
20:52:53,460 --> 20:52:55,090
What's happening?

622
20:52:55,300 --> 20:52:57,186
They arrested Alice Morgan.

623
20:52:57,643 --> 20:52:59,340
Where is she?

624
20:53:02,700 --> 20:53:05,062
- And Mary?
- She left you a message.

625
20:53:09,980 --> 20:53:11,499
She gave you this?

626
20:53:11,500 --> 20:53:13,172
She put it into my hand herself.

627
20:53:15,940 --> 20:53:17,660
Benny, I appreciate it, pal.

628
20:53:22,500 --> 20:53:24,390
Where you going, boss? She went that way.

629
20:53:24,700 --> 20:53:26,620
I just want to say sorry to Alice.

630
20:53:49,660 --> 20:53:54,363
There's been a mix up over who's who.

631
20:53:54,921 --> 20:53:56,448
I expect they'll, er,

632
20:53:57,643 --> 20:54:00,421
