633
20:54:03,136 --> 20:54:05,908
I don't care what she's done,

634
20:54:06,865 --> 20:54:08,010
John.

635
20:54:09,348 --> 20:54:10,969
She saved my life.

636
20:54:16,740 --> 20:54:18,441
So you should probably...

637
20:54:18,829 --> 20:54:19,980
go.

638
20:54:22,540 --> 20:54:23,934
Yeah.

639
20:54:24,660 --> 20:54:25,818
Yeah.

640
20:54:26,260 --> 20:54:27,540
I should do that.

641
20:54:39,460 --> 20:54:41,790
- I...
- I know.

642
20:54:43,540 --> 20:54:44,849
Me too.

643
20:54:59,260 --> 20:55:01,260
Go on. Go.

644
20:56:51,060 --> 20:56:53,419
It was clever. The choice you made.

645
20:56:57,940 --> 20:56:59,237
Marwood?

646
20:57:00,075 --> 20:57:01,226
Alive.

647
20:57:01,558 --> 20:57:03,084
Suffering.

648
20:57:03,585 --> 20:57:05,168
Good.

